     File: Minimal/Colors.xaml
     Author: Derek Tremblay (derektremblay666@gmail.com)
     Contributors: Claude (Anthropic)
     Created: 2026-03-06
     Description:
         Color token definitions for the Minimal theme. Ultra-clean monochrome
         palette with pure white backgrounds, light gray borders, and near-black
         text. No accent colors — maximum visual simplicity.

     Architecture Notes:
         ResourceDictionary. Consumed as the first merged dictionary in MinimalTheme.xaml.
         Defines all Dock* and Panel_* keys required by Light/ shared templates
         and PanelCommon.xaml.
     ========================================================== -->

